sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as EvalHub Operator
    participant Job as LMES Job Container<br/>(Kubernetes Job)
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Model as Model Inference Endpoint<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry (Quay)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Tracking<br/>HTTPS

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Operator,Job: Flow 1: Online Evaluation Job Execution
        Operator->>Job: Create K8s Job<br/>ServiceAccount auth
        Note over Job: Load /meta/job.json<br/>Parse job spec
        Job->>EvalHub: POST callback: phase=Initializing<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
        Job->>HFHub: GET datasets & tokenizers<br/>HF_TOKEN (optional), TLS 1.2+
        HFHub-->>Job: Benchmark data & tokenizer files
        Job->>EvalHub: POST callback: phase=Running<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+

        loop For each benchmark task batch
            Job->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>Bearer Token (OPENAI_API_KEY)<br/>TLS configurable, up to 128 concurrent
            Model-->>Job: Completion/logprob responses
            Job->>EvalHub: POST callback: progress update<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
        end

        Note over Job: Compute metrics<br/>(accuracy, BLEU, F1, etc.)
        Job->>EvalHub: POST callback: phase=Complete<br/>Results payload, Bearer Token
        Job->>OCI: Push OCI artifact (skopeo)<br/>Registry auth, TLS 1.2+
        Job->>MLflow: POST metrics & parameters<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Operator,Job: Flow 2: Offline/Disconnected Evaluation
        participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant InitC as Init Container

        Operator->>Job: Create K8s Job<br/>(offline=true)
        InitC->>S3: GET pre-staged test data<br/>AWS IAM / IBM COS, TLS 1.2+
        S3-->>InitC: Test data artifacts
        InitC->>InitC: Write to /test_data volume

        Note over Job: HF_HUB_OFFLINE=1<br/>HF_DATASETS_OFFLINE=1<br/>HF_HOME=/test_data
        Job->>Job: Load datasets from /test_data<br/>Load metrics from metrics/

        loop For each benchmark task batch
            Job->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>Bearer Token, TLS configurable
            Model-->>Job: Completion/logprob responses
        end

        Job->>EvalHub: POST callback: results<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
    end
